36:33.525 --> 36:34.567
How do you plead?

36:37.612 --> 36:38.946
Not guilty.

38:22.634 --> 38:23.676
Well, look here.

38:23.760 --> 38:26.136
I wasn't expecting
to see you beauties.

38:27.097 --> 38:29.473
