isn't new to Camille,

38:40.610 --> 38:42.194
but it is new to you.

38:42.946 --> 38:44.238
It's a new lease.

38:45.740 --> 38:48.117
You know, I might just come up
to St. Louis one day

38:48.243 --> 38:49.785
for a visit.

38:49.869 --> 38:51.245
Yeah, you should do that.

38:54.082 --> 38:56.625
Do not let that witch
come to St. Louis.

38:57.335 --> 38:59.837
