because I have Adora's sickness?

40:01.608 --> 40:03.984
"I waver between the two.

40:04.861 --> 40:08.822
"Especially at night,
when my skin begins to pulse.

40:10.408 --> 40:12.117
"Lately, I've been...

40:14.496 --> 40:16.622
"Leaning toward kindness."

