She seems like
she's gonna be just fine.

41:36.828 --> 41:38.745
And I like her friend.

41:39.497 --> 41:41.582
She might actually be
a good influence on her.

41:43.418 --> 41:45.836
Amma's, I don't know.

41:45.920 --> 41:48.172
She doesn't sleep most nights
unless I'm with her.

41:50.425 --> 41:52.968
-She misses Adora.
-What a thing.

41:53.595 --> 41:56.763
Even when you win
the fucked-up family Olympics...

41:57.765 --> 42:00.517
Okay, guys, time to eat now.

42:04.147 --> 42:05.189
It's about damn time!

