42:47.482 --> 42:50.609
- I do not.
- Kiss-ass.

42:51.402 --> 42:53.278
I don't know what
I want to do yet, exactly.

42:53.363 --> 42:55.322
- We have a lot of time, right?
- Absolutely.

42:55.406 --> 42:58.492
Well, I'm gonna be
an on-camera personality.

42:58.576 --> 43:01.245
I have the gift of gab, that's what...

43:01.329 --> 43:02.829
